## Gateway & Network Configuration — UniFi ({{ platforms.gateway.model }})

> **Note on Unifi UI navigation:** Ubiquiti frequently reorganizes the Unifi
> Network application between versions. The navigation paths below were verified
> on **Unifi Network {{ platforms.gateway.version | default('10.x') }}**. If a
> menu item is not where described, search for the feature name in the Settings
