- [ ] **DHCP DNS servers** — set to the per-environment DNS server IPs, NOT the gateway:
  - DNS Server 1: `{{ vms.dns1_dev.ip }}` (dns1-dev)
  - DNS Server 2: `{{ vms.dns2_dev.ip }}` (dns2-dev)

  > **UI path (UniFi Network {{ platforms.gateway.version | default('10.x') }}):**
  > **Settings → Networks → Dev → DHCP → DHCP Service Management →**
  > scroll down to **DNS Server** and switch from "Auto" to "Manual", then
  > enter the two DNS server IPs above.

  > **WARNING:** Do NOT leave DNS set to "Auto" or use the gateway IP
  > (`{{ environments.dev.gateway }}`). The gateway does not serve the
  > per-environment DNS zones. VMs would fail to resolve internal hostnames
  > like `influxdb.dev.{{ domain }}` and unqualified names like `influxdb`
  > would not resolve at all. This is the setting that makes
  > `dig +search vault` from inside a VM resolve to the correct
